Class ImagePanelWithClass

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class ImagePanelWithClass
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    This class is an image-holding panel that also displays the class-affiliation information as a colored frame around the image.
